                    <h2>Summary</h2>
                    <!-- My testimonial here -->
                    <p>This project represented a significant individual contributionâ€”I implemented approximately 90% of the application independently, encompassing both backend architecture and frontend development. The design collaboration produced a visually striking platform that effectively showcases the client's premium roofing products.</p>

                    <p>The technical foundation leverages our custom <a href="https://github.com/flex360/pilot" target="_blank">FLEX360 CMS</a> built on Laravel, providing administrators with full CRUD capabilities across all content models. I architected the database schema, implemented RESTful controllers, and connected data models to the polished frontend views.</p>

